description.author: Henning Thielemann, Stefan Kersten, Soenke Hahn <soenkehahn@gmail.com>
description.synopsis: Bindings for the JACK Audio Connection Kit
description.description:
Bindings for the JACK Audio Connection Kit <http://jackaudio.org/>.
It has support both for PCM audio and MIDI handling.

In order to adapt to your system,
you may have to disable pkgConfig or jackFree cabal flags.

You should compile your clients with @ghc --make -O2 -threaded ...@

package-flags.name: pkgconfig
package-flags.description: Use pkg-config tool for check version and presence of jack
